headline: Cboe Conducts First European Retail Investor Survey; Indicates Strong Demand for European Equity Options and Trusted Financial Education
summary: Cboe Global Markets, Inc. (Cboe: CBOE), the world's leading derivatives and securities exchange network, today announced the results of its inaugural survey of European retail investors, conducted jointly by Cboe Europe Derivatives (CEDX), Cboe's pan-European equity derivatives marketplace, and The Options Institute, Cboe's education arm.
